===== Lobbies and outposts =====
Similarly to [[City|cities]], lobbies and outposts are mostly combat-free open-world areas with various [[service]]s. However, they are often smaller, they often don't have map completion, and they tend to serve as staging points for specific game modes or activities. The main permanently available lobbies and outposts in PvE are:

