===== Public instances =====
[[Public instance]]s are special large-scale instances which can be entered in two distinct versions. ''Public'' versions function similarly to open-world zones, where you can enter them and will be randomly matched up with other players, but they tend to only be open for entry this way at [[Event timers|specific times]] during the day. Alternatively, a [[squad]] can at any time open a ''private'' version that cannot be entered by other players. These zones typically revolve around completing a series of events and killing a boss. This system is used for some [[#Raids|raid encounters]] and [[#Dragon Response Missions|Dragon Response Missions]], as well as the following zones:

