===== Lounges =====
[[Lounge]]s are exclusive convenience areas with various services and portals to other areas. They usually require an item purchased from the {{gem}} [[Gem Store]] to enter. Most lounges are located within other zones but some have their own instances. (See [[Lounge]] for their full list and comparison.)
