==== Guild instances ====
; Guild Halls
[[Guild hall]]s are zones owned by a [[guild]] where its members can meet and socialize. They must be captured by the guild first, and afterwards they can be upgraded and decorated. They also appear on the world map.

Players taking part in the capture event must have their respective expansion unlocked, but afterwards they can be accessed by all accounts.
